$lang['Similarly, after reaching 9 in Hexadecimal (represented by “F”), we start counting again at 10 (“10”). This pattern continues until we reach 15 (“1F”), at which point we reset back to 0 and begin counting again at 16 (“20”). This might sound confusing at first, but with a little practice, it will become second nature!'] = 'San aon dòigh, às deidh dhuinn 9 a ruighinn ann an Hexadecimal (air a riochdachadh le “F”), bidh sinn a’ tòiseachadh a ’cunntadh a-rithist aig 10 (“10”). Leanaidh am pàtran seo gus an ruig sinn 15 (“1F”), agus aig an àm sin bidh sinn ag ath-shuidheachadh air ais gu 0 agus a’ tòiseachadh a’ cunntadh a-rithist aig 16 (“20”). Is dòcha gu bheil seo troimh-chèile an toiseach, ach le beagan cleachdaidh, bidh e na dhàrna nàdar!';
