$lang['You can use hexadecimal to convert between decimal and binary values. For example, converting 10011011001010 into hexadecimal would result in 0x4F. This means that the value 4F represents the binary number 100110110010110.'] = 'Faodaidh tu hexadecimal a chleachdadh gus tionndadh eadar luachan deicheach agus dà-chànanach. Mar eisimpleir, le bhith ag atharrachadh 10011011001010 gu hexadecimal bhiodh 0x4F. Tha seo a’ ciallachadh gu bheil an luach 4F a’ riochdachadh an àireamh binary 100110110010110.';
$lang['In mathematics and computer science, hexadecimal (also base 16, or hex) is a positional numeral system with a radix, or base, of 16. It uses sixteen distinct symbols, most often the symbols 0–9 to represent values zero to nine, and A, B, C, D, E, F (or alternatively a–f) to represent values ten to fifteen. For example, the hexadecimal number 2AF3 is equal, in decimal, to (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) , or 10,995.'] = 'Ann am matamataig agus saidheans coimpiutaireachd, &#39;s e siostam àireamhach suidheachaidh a th&#39; ann an heicsidheach (cuideachd bonn 16, neo heics) le radix, no bonn, de 16. Bidh e a&#39; cleachdadh sia-deug samhlaidhean sònraichte, mar as trice na samhlaidhean 0–9 gus luachan neoni gu naoi a riochdachadh, agus A, B, C, D, E, F (no air an làimh eile a–f) gus luachan a riochdachadh deich gu còig-deug. Mar eisimpleir, tha an àireamh heicsidheach 2AF3 co-ionann, ann an deicheach, gu (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160), no 10,995.';
$lang['Each hexadecimal digit represents four binary digits (bits) (also called a "nibble"), and the primary use of hexadecimal notation is as a human-friendly representation of binary coded values in computing and digital electronics. For example, byte values can range from 0 to 255 (decimal) but may be more conveniently represented as two hexadecimal digits in the range 00 through FF. Hexadecimal is also commonly used to represent computer memory addresses.'] = 'Tha gach figear hexadecimal a’ riochdachadh ceithir àireamhan dà-chànanach (bitean) (ris an canar cuideachd “nibble”), agus tha am prìomh chleachdadh de chomharradh hexadecimal mar riochdachadh càirdeil dha daoine de luachan còd dà-chànanach ann an coimpiutaireachd agus electronics didseatach. Mar eisimpleir, faodaidh luachan byte a bhith eadar 0 agus 255 (deicheach) ach dh’ fhaodadh iad a bhith air an riochdachadh nas freagarraiche mar dà fhigear hexadecimal anns an raon 00 tro FF. Tha hexadecimal cuideachd air a chleachdadh gu cumanta airson seòlaidhean cuimhne coimpiutair a riochdachadh.';
$lang['Hex is an abbreviation of Hexadecimal, which is based on a base -16 structure and is used for simplifying how instructions to computers are represented. This 16 symbols number system was developed as a means of inhibiting an 8-bit binary number, so data can be encoded into computers effortlessly. It can be imprinted and typed using two different hex digits with each hex digit demonstrating a nibble or perhaps a 4-bits format.'] = 'Tha Hex na ghiorrachadh de Hexadecimal, a tha stèidhichte air structar bonn -16 agus air a chleachdadh airson a bhith a’ sìmpleachadh mar a tha stiùireadh do choimpiutairean air an riochdachadh. Chaidh an siostam àireamh samhlaidhean 16 seo a leasachadh mar dhòigh air casg a chuir air àireamh binary 8-bit, gus an urrainnear dàta a chòdachadh gu coimpiutairean gun oidhirp. Faodar a chlò-bhualadh agus a chlò-bhualadh le bhith a’ cleachdadh dà fhigear hex eadar-dhealaichte le gach figear hex a’ sealltainn cruth nibble no is dòcha 4-bit.';
$lang['This number system uses 16 symbols that are represented in a range from 0-9 or A-F. The 0–9 represent numbers up to nine whereas A-F is represented by the numeric 10–15. As compared to the other three types of number systems, the hexadecimal numeral system is considered to be the most effective one.'] = 'Bidh an siostam àireamh seo a’ cleachdadh 16 samhlaidhean a tha air an riochdachadh ann an raon bho 0-9 no AF. Tha an 0–9 a’ riochdachadh àireamhan suas gu naoi ach tha AF air a riochdachadh leis an àireamh 10–15. An coimeas ris na trì seòrsachan eile de shiostaman àireamh, thathas den bheachd gur e an siostam àireamhach hexadecimal am fear as èifeachdaiche.';
$lang['Your hexadecimal code is invalid'] = 'Tha an còd hexadecimal agad neo-dhligheach';
